16 bool GeometricKinematic::rcmCallback(masterslave::GeometricKinematicRCM::Request &req, masterslave::GeometricKinematicRCM::Response &resp)
17 {
18  Eigen::Affine3d T_0_FL;
19  tf::poseMsgToEigen(req.T_0_FL,T_0_FL);
20  RCM = T_0_FL * buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d(TOOL_PARAMETERS.X_RCM,TOOL_PARAMETERS.Y_0_Q4,TOOL_PARAMETERS.Z_0_Q4),Eigen::Vector3d(TOOL_PARAMETERS.A_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD,TOOL_PARAMETERS.B_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD,TOOL_PARAMETERS.C_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD),true);
21  tf::poseEigenToMsg(RCM,resp.trocar);
22  ROS_WARN_STREAM(RCM.translation());
23  return true;
24 }

26 bool GeometricKinematic::directKinematicsCallback(masterslave::GeometricKinematicDirectKinematics::Request &req, masterslave::GeometricKinematicDirectKinematics::Response &resp)
27 {
28  Eigen::Affine3d T_0_FL;

48 Eigen::Affine3d GeometricKinematic::calcDirKin(Eigen::VectorXd jointAngles)
49 {
50  T_FL_Q4 = buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d(TOOL_PARAMETERS.X_0_Q4,TOOL_PARAMETERS.Y_0_Q4,TOOL_PARAMETERS.Z_0_Q4),Eigen::Vector3d(TOOL_PARAMETERS.A_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD,TOOL_PARAMETERS.B_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD,TOOL_PARAMETERS.C_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD),true);
51  T_FL_Q4.rotate(Eigen::AngleAxis<double>(jointAngles(0),Eigen::Vector3d::UnitZ()));
52  Eigen::Affine3d T_Q4_Q5 = buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d::Zero(),Eigen::Vector3d(90*DEG_TO_RAD,0,90*DEG_TO_RAD+jointAngles(1)),false);
53  /* Fehler: Zuerst um Q5 drehen, dann verschieben */
54  Eigen::Affine3d T_Q5_Q6 = buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d(TOOL_PARAMETERS.L_Q5_Q6,0,0),Eigen::Vector3d(-90*DEG_TO_RAD,0,0),true);
55  Eigen::Affine3d T_Q6_EE = buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d::Zero(),Eigen::Vector3d(0,0,jointAngles(2)),true);
56  T_Q6_EE.translate(Eigen::Vector3d(TOOL_PARAMETERS.L_Q6_EE,0,0));
57 
58  T_FL_Q5 = T_FL_Q4*T_Q4_Q5;
59  T_FL_Q6 = T_FL_Q5*T_Q5_Q6;
60 
61  return T_FL_EE = T_FL_Q4*T_Q4_Q5*T_Q5_Q6*T_Q6_EE;
62 }

65 bool GeometricKinematic::calcInvKin(Eigen::Affine3d desEEPosition)
66 {
67  ROS_INFO_STREAM("desEEPosition: \n" << desEEPosition.matrix());
68  ROS_INFO_STREAM("RCM: \n" << RCM.matrix());
69  Eigen::Affine3d T_0_Q6 = desEEPosition.translate(Eigen::Vector3d(-TOOL_PARAMETERS.L_Q6_EE,0,0));
70  Eigen::Vector3d p_RCM_Q6 = T_0_Q6.translation()-RCM.translation();
71  Eigen::Vector3d z_Q6 = T_0_Q6.matrix().col(2).head(3);
72  Eigen::Vector3d nPlane = p_RCM_Q6.cross(z_Q6);
73 
74  Eigen::Vector3d y_Q6 = -T_0_Q6.matrix().col(1).head(3);
75 
76  jointAnglesTar(2) = acos(nPlane.dot(y_Q6)/(nPlane.norm()*y_Q6.norm()));
77 
78  if(isnan(jointAnglesTar(2)))
79  {
80  jointAnglesTar(2) = 0.0;
81  }
82 
83  if(jointAnglesTar(2)>M_PI/2)
84  {
85  jointAnglesTar(2) = M_PI/2;
86  }
87 
88  if(nPlane.cross(y_Q6).dot(z_Q6)<0)
89  {
90  jointAnglesTar(2) = -jointAnglesTar(2);
91  }
92  ROS_INFO_STREAM(jointAnglesTar(2));
93  Eigen::Affine3d T_EE_Q5 = buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d::Zero(),Eigen::Vector3d(90*DEG_TO_RAD,0,-jointAnglesTar(2)),true);
94  T_EE_Q5.translate(Eigen::Vector3d(-TOOL_PARAMETERS.L_Q5_Q6,0,0));
95  Eigen::Affine3d T_0_Q5 = desEEPosition*T_EE_Q5;
96  ROS_INFO_STREAM("T_0_Q5" << T_0_Q5.matrix());
97 
98  Eigen::Vector3d z_Q5 = T_0_Q5.matrix().col(2).head(3);
99 
100  Eigen::Vector3d y_Q5 = -T_0_Q5.matrix().col(1).head(3);
101 
102  Eigen::Vector3d p_Q5_RCM = T_0_Q5.translation() - RCM.translation();
103 
104  Eigen::Vector3d x_Q4 = p_Q5_RCM.cross(z_Q5);
105 
106  jointAnglesTar(1) = acos(x_Q4.dot(y_Q5)/(x_Q4.norm()*y_Q5.norm()));
107  ROS_INFO_STREAM("Q5:\n" << jointAnglesTar(1));
108 
109  if(isnan(jointAnglesTar(1)))
110  {
111  jointAnglesTar(1) = 0.0;
112  }
113 
114  /*if(jointAnglesTar(1)>M_PI/2)
115  {
116  jointAnglesTar(1) = M_PI/2;
117  }*/
118 
119  if(x_Q4.cross(y_Q5).dot(z_Q5)<0)
120  {
121  jointAnglesTar(1) = -jointAnglesTar(1);
122  }
123 
124  Eigen::Affine3d T_Q5_Q4 = buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d::Zero(),Eigen::Vector3d(-90*DEG_TO_RAD,0,-90*DEG_TO_RAD-jointAnglesTar(1)),true);
125  T_0_Q4 = T_0_Q5*T_Q5_Q4;
126  ROS_INFO_STREAM("T_0_Q4: \n" << T_0_Q4.matrix());
127 
128  Eigen::Vector3d p_Q4_RCM = T_0_Q4.translation() - RCM.translation();
129 
130  Eigen::Vector3d y_FL = T_0_FL.matrix().col(1).head(3);
131 
132  Eigen::Vector3d z_FL = y_FL.cross(p_Q4_RCM);
133 
134  jointAnglesTar(0) = acos(z_FL.dot(x_Q4)/(z_FL.norm()*x_Q4.norm()));
135 
136  if(isnan(jointAnglesTar(0)))
137  {
138  jointAnglesTar(0) = 0.0;
139  }
140 
141  if(z_FL.cross(x_Q4).dot(p_Q4_RCM)<0)
142  {
143  jointAnglesTar(0) = -jointAnglesTar(0);
144  }
145 
146  Eigen::Affine3d T_Q4_FL = buildAffine3d(Eigen::Vector3d::Zero(),Eigen::Vector3d(-TOOL_PARAMETERS.A_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD,-TOOL_PARAMETERS.B_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD,-TOOL_PARAMETERS.C_0_Q4*DEG_TO_RAD-jointAnglesTar(0)),true);
147  T_Q4_FL.translate(Eigen::Vector3d(-TOOL_PARAMETERS.X_0_Q4,-TOOL_PARAMETERS.Y_0_Q4,-TOOL_PARAMETERS.Z_0_Q4));
148  T_0_FL = T_0_Q4*T_Q4_FL;
149 }

151 Eigen::Affine3d GeometricKinematic::buildAffine3d(const Eigen::Vector3d &translXYZ, const Eigen::Vector3d &axisZYX, bool zyx=true)
152 {
153  Eigen::Affine3d transl;
154  transl.setIdentity();
155  transl.translate(translXYZ);
156  if(zyx)
157  {
158  transl.rotate(Eigen::AngleAxis<double>(axisZYX(2), Eigen::Vector3d::UnitZ()));
159  transl.rotate(Eigen::AngleAxis<double>(axisZYX(1), Eigen::Vector3d::UnitY()));
160  transl.rotate(Eigen::AngleAxis<double>(axisZYX(0), Eigen::Vector3d::UnitX()));
161  }
162  else
163  {
164  transl.rotate(Eigen::AngleAxis<double>(axisZYX(0), Eigen::Vector3d::UnitX()));
165  transl.rotate(Eigen::AngleAxis<double>(axisZYX(1), Eigen::Vector3d::UnitY()));
166  transl.rotate(Eigen::AngleAxis<double>(axisZYX(2), Eigen::Vector3d::UnitZ()));
167  }
168  return transl;
169 }
